<i>noun</i>: 일주 [일쭈], 순회 [순회/순훼], 순방 [순방], 견학 [견ː학] <i>verb</i>: 유람하다 [유람하다], 순회하다 [순회하다/순훼하다], 순방하다 [순방하다], 견학하다 [견ː하카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>일주 [일쭈]</dt><br>
<dd>tour; round; traveling around</dd><br>
<dd>일정한 길을 따라 한 바퀴 돎.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of circling along a certain route.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>순회 [순회/순훼]</dt><br>
<dd>rounds; tour</dd><br>
<dd>여러 곳을 차례로 돌아다님.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of going around several places sequentially.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>순방 [순방]</dt><br>
<dd>visit; tour</dd><br>
<dd>여러 나라나 도시 등을 차례로 돌아가며 찾아감.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of visiting several countries, cities, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>견학 [견ː학]</dt><br>
<dd>field trip; tour</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일과 관련된 곳을 직접 찾아가서 보고 배움.</dd><br>
<dd>Learning by visiting the place related to a certain subject.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>유람하다 [유람하다]</dt><br>
<dd>go sightseeing; tour</dd><br>
<dd>여러 곳을 돌아다니며 구경하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To go to places and look around.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>순회하다 [순회하다/순훼하다]</dt><br>
<dd>go round; tour</dd><br>
<dd>여러 곳을 차례로 돌아다니다.</dd><br>
<dd>To go around several places sequentially.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>순방하다 [순방하다]</dt><br>
<dd>visit; tour</dd><br>
<dd>여러 나라나 도시 등을 차례로 돌아가며 찾아가다.</dd><br>
<dd>To visit several countries, cities, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>견학하다 [견ː하카다]</dt><br>
<dd>go on a field trip; visit; tour</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일과 관련된 곳을 직접 찾아가서 보고 배우다.</dd><br>
<dd>To learn by visiting a place related to a certain subject.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>